    "body" : "<p>OutputStream writes bytes, String provides chars. You need to define Charset to encode string to byte[]:</p>\n\n<pre><code>outputStream.write(string.getBytes(Charset.forName(\"UTF-8\")));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Change <code>UTF-8</code> to a charset of your choice.</p>\n"
