    "body" : "<p><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/io/OutputStreamWriter.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">By design</a> it is to be done this way:</p>\n\n<pre><code>OutputStream out = ...;\ntry (Writer w = new OutputStreamWriter(out, \"UTF-8\")) {\n    w.write(\"Hello, World!\");\n} // or w.close(); //close will auto-flush\n</code></pre>\n"
